{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f4972b589c","title":"毛泽东给张治中的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f37a100ea0","index":0,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":22,"articleId":"f4972b589c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6ed879d96d","type":"title","text":"毛泽东给张治中的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4972b589c"},{"id":"b63b9c6188","type":"paragraph","text":"文白先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4972b589c"},{"id":"357388ff29","type":"paragraph","text":"五月三日的信早已收到。原封不动，直至今天，打开一看，一口气读完了《六十岁总结》，感到高兴。我的高兴，不是在你的世界观方面。在这方面，我们是有距离的。高兴是在作品的气氛方面，是在使人能看到作者的心的若干点方面，是在你还有向前进取的意愿方面。我猜想，这一年多的时间内，害苦了你，一个老人遇到这样的大风浪。这种心情，我是理解的。觅暇当约大驾一谈。这几天尚不可能。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4972b589c"},{"id":"3b1a97edb6","type":"paragraph","text":"祝安好！问候你的夫人和孩子们！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4972b589c"},{"id":"201da9cc65","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东五月二十二日上午七时","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4972b589c"}],"page":{"id":"bc98b47cb1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"f4972b589c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}